But now, with Jacks new server, I’m just going for it! Feel free to follow! I follow from @theblogifollowfromformysideblog and I’m in the server as the same name I’ve got for this blog but my actual discord tag is zane/Akiiki#6093
RB this if you post youtuber content (especially mark and jack)! I wanna follow you!
